This story is in OOC!  It's about my epic raid against Venril Sathir's Remains and the aftermath.  Also, the raid was for my new friend Melba also. Here goes, I hope you like it!<br>
<br>
Melba has slain Venril Sathir! (I was grinning....And cheering, this time I didn't jump up in down in my seat, because I've seen VS go down plenty!)<br>
Various shouts, 'WOOT! Congrats Zantes and Melba!'<br>
You tell Melba, 'Alrighty!  That's how we do it!'<br>
I had raided VSR 9 times, on the 10th is when I finally got my epic stone!  Melba needed a stone to progress in her epic up to the sky stone.  I had &quot;claimed&quot; venril sathir's remains about 8 minutes before Melba waltzed in and claimed it <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   I talked to her and told her my guild was coming in to help.  Since nobody had piped up about the second stone, I told her she would be more than welcome to loot it!  She was VERY happy.<br>
<br>
After the fight, people were porting and being xloc'd outta the pit.  The &quot;funny&quot; thing was, a group of us, 7 or 8, got left behind in the pit.  Shoogie, our &quot;pacifist sorcerer&quot; or the druid in his grouped casted succor to the zoneline.  <br>
<br>
Cromondas, Charnishher, Engell, Vintara, Sudaien, and I were left behind.  I started biznatchin at Shoogie to run back down there, I think he purposly took his time ;-)  At any rate it was fun &quot;fighting for our lives while we waited for help!&quot;  <br>
<br>
I then told the group in the pit, &quot;I should write a story about us being trapped!&quot;  They seemed to like the idea.  <br>
<br>
Although the raid wasn't really classified by FoV as a raid...Why? Because Kenshu didn't die..in fact, Kenshu didn't even attend, so it was just basically it was 20 people lookin for a good time killin the old iksar king <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   <br>
<br>
Cromondas, however, DID die.  That was the compensation in Kenshu's place.<br>
<br>
THE END<br>
<br>
It wasn't a roleplaying story really, but it was a story told by the human player playing the Half elf!  I'm not really sure if this is a rave or just me rambling...AT ANY RATE! Thank you to all the raiders, to Brios for forming groups, to melba for getting that nice erudite cleric <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
Later all!<br>
